title: Hello Paradise: Sumbawa Episode 2
description: watching your friends drop into these waves was a raw adrenaline rush that would leave you holding your breath until you saw them paddle back out to you... deep blue water, shallow reef, good company, the best me-goreng you'll ever eat, bumpy car rides, music and spontaneous dance parties, hunting for shells, these are a few of the things that made the trip so special for me - alessa
